reviews.review_text: I was in on Monday and was greeted and served by Sophia. I had the best time ever! The room was clean and even had a shower to use before and after the treatment. I booked a one hour treatment. The massage was very thorough and very good. Like in any other establishment of this kind the girl wants to upsell the service when you are most vulnerable and decide with the wrong head! I agreed to a service and let me tell you what followed was worth every nickel and dime spent and even more. It was the best service that I had in my over 60 years experience. I will definitely be back to see Sophia the next time Im in the city! Highly recommended!

I ve had the best experience with Bonnie. I highly recommend her. She has a very authentic, pure, great personality and overall a very positive energy. Would definitely recommend this place. Definitely will not be my last  visit. In strong hopes to revisit and enjoy what this place has to offer furthermore. Keep it up!!
